Source location: git@github.com:devtank-ltd/hiltop_motherboard.git 

As per CERN-OHL-W v2 section 4.1, should You produce hardware based on these sources, You must maintain the   Source Location visible on the external case of the HILTOP or other product you make using this documentation.

This folder contains a reference HILTOP plug-in card design schematics & PCB layout. You may use this design as a starting template for developing new plug-in modules for HILTOP.

You will need Kicad to open hardware design files.

HILTOP products and other test and measurement solutions can be purchased directly from Devtank Ltd.

